0007               ***************************************************************
0008               * bl  @pane.cmdb.statlines
0009               *--------------------------------------------------------------
0010               * INPUT
0011               * @tv.devpath      = Pointer to string with device path
0012               * @tv.sams.maxpage = Number of SAMS pages in system
0013               * @tv.sams.hipage  = Highest page in use
0014               *--------------------------------------------------------------
0015               * OUTPUT
0016               * @ram.msg1 = SAMS free status line
0017               * @ram.msg2 = Device path status line
0018               *--------------------------------------------------------------
0019               * Register usage
0020               * tmp0,tmp1,tmp2
0021               ********|*****|*********************|**************************
0022               pane.cmdb.statlines:
0023 6CEC 0649  14         dect  stack
